bourne:export.description: Exports records from the object specified.
examples:
$ sfdx bourne:export -o Product2 -u myOrg -c config/cpq-cli-def.json
    Requesting data, please wait.... Request completed! Received X records.

loglevel.name: loglevel
loglevel.description: logging level for this command invocation

targetusername.name: targetusername
targetusername.description: username or alias for the target org; overrides default target org

apiversion.name: apiversion
apiversion.description: override the api version used for api requests made by this command

object.name: object
object.description: The sobject that you wish to import/export reference data from.

processall.name: processall
processall.description: Exports records from all objects specified in the config file.

bourne:import.description: Imports records from the object specified.
examples:
$ sfdx bourne:import -o Product2 -u myOrg -c config/cpq-cli-def.json
    Deploying data, please wait.... Deployment completed!
